in contrast to the in-vivo data AT-III increased significantly from
113.5% at baseline to 117% after 4 days (n = 10, P-value= 0.02; Table 2).")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000114> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000175> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000121>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000175> "A quantitative confidence value that represents the probability of obtaining a result at least as extreme as that actually obtained, assuming that the actual value was the result of chance alone."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000175> "May be outside the scope of OBI long term, is needed so is retained")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000175> "PERSON:Chris Stoeckert"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000175> "p-value"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000175> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000071>)

