AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000181> "1/28/2013, BP, on the call it was raised that we may want to switch to an external ontology for all populatin terms: 
