# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> (analyte role)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "Glucose in blood (measured in an assay to determine the concentration of glucose).")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000114> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000122>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "A measurand role borne by a molecular entity or an atom and realized in an analyte assay which achieves the objective to measure the magnitude/concentration/amount of the analyte in the entity bearing evaluant role."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "interestingly, an analyte is still an analyte even if it is not detected.  for this reason it does not bear a specified input role")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "pH (technically the inverse log of [H+]) may be considered a quality; this remains to be tested.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "qualities such as weight, color are not assayed but measured, so they do not fall into this category.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "GROUP: Role Branch")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000232> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "Feb 10, 2009.  changes after discussion at OBI Consortium Workshop Feb 2-6, 2009.  accepted as core term.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> "analyte role"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002444>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000275> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000081> ObjectUnionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000011> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000013>)))

