# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000372> (material separation function)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000114> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000372> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000122>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000372> "A material separation function is a function that increases the resolution between two or more material entities. The  to distinction between the entities is usually based on some associated physical quality."@en)
