AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000114> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000376> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000122>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000376> "A synthesizing function is a function to assemble new output materials from distinct input materials.  The output materials typically consist of chemically distinct monomeric objects or object aggregate polymers."@en)
