AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000232> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0400112> "DS: Is this class justified? Its a unnamed class. If so, put a fluidic_system and the fluidic_subsystem as subclasses. TW: This is required by MO. FG: Or as function.")
