# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> (administering substance in vivo)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "Balb/c mice received an intracameral or subconjunctival injection of trinitrophenylated spleen cells")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "injecting mice with 10 ug morphine intranasally, a patient taking two pills of 1 mg aspirin orally"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000114> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000125>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "A process by which a substance is intentionally given to an organism resulting in exposure of the organism to that substance."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "2009-11-10. Tracker: https://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=detail&aid=2893050&group_id=177891&atid=886178")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "Different routes and means of administration should go as children underneath this"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "Update the definition based on the discussion. Details see the tracker:
https://sourceforge.net/p/obi/obi-terms/738/")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "needs roles such as perturber and perturbee (children of input role). Perturb is too strong. Host might be the name for one role. Others considered: Doner, Donated, Acceptor."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "Bjoern Peters"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "Person:Bjoern Peters")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600007> "administering substance in vivo"@en)
