AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0600038> "The addition of phycoerytherin label to an anti-CD8 antibody, to label all antibodies. The addition of anti-CD8-PE to a population of cells, to label the subpopulation cells that are CD8+."@en)
